## 📊 Monitoring

The Observer agent provides real-time monitoring:

```python
# Get system status
status = await observer.execute_task(
    TaskRequest(capability="system_monitoring")
)

# Get recent events
events = await observer.execute_task(
    TaskRequest(
        capability="event_logging",
        parameters={"limit": 50}
    )
)

# Get performance metrics
metrics = await observer.execute_task(
    TaskRequest(capability="metrics_reporting")
)
```

## 🔐 Security

- ✅ All credentials via environment variables
- ✅ No hardcoded secrets
- ✅ Pydantic validation for all inputs
- ✅ Secure AWS credential handling
- ✅ `.gitignore` configured for sensitive files

